# Docker instructions

Clone

    git clone https://github.com/bibstha/bharkhar-downloader.git
    cd bharkhar-downloader
    docker build --rm -t bharkharapp .
    
Start a docker data volume by

    docker run -v /data -name DATA tianon/true

Start the docker container for sidekiq workers and sshd

    docker run -d --name bharkharapp -p 127.0.0.1:4567:4567 -p 127.0.0.1:49122:22 --volumes-from DATA bharkharapp


